        <title>交互作品《鱼与星河》作品介绍</title>
        <link>https://lumistarry.github.io/p/%E4%BA%A4%E4%BA%92%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E9%B1%BC%E4%B8%8E%E6%98%9F%E6%B2%B3%E4%BD%9C%E5%93%81%E4%BB%8B%E7%BB%8D/</link>
